          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1645551084223-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has slightly softened, add the<strong> spinach</strong>, <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> and <strong>honey mirin sauce</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min further or until the spinach has wilted and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Japanese-style chicken & sugar snap stir-fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1645551104114-x200.jpg",
