            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, squeeze the pouch<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> of <strong>steamed white rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> (just a little!) and <strong>microwave</strong> for 3 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
